        map.put("Bull Market", new ArrayList<>(Arrays.asList("When the stock market as a whole is in a prolonged period of increasing stock prices. It’s the opposite of a bear market. A single stock can be bullish or bearish too, as can a sector, which I’ll describe later on.","Question", "me?", "me?", "me?", "me?", "B")));
